The '''Goblin guard''' is a [[monster]] encountered during the [[Observatory Quest]]. He guards the kitchen in which the [[lens mould]] is found. The keep key must be obtained from a chest in the dungeon and he must be killed in order to enter the keep.

==Locations==
*[[Observatory dungeon]]

